        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "They departed not from the commandment of the king — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "He obeyed God’s commands enjoined by David, in God’s name, and by inspiration of God’s Spirit, and therefore all obeyed his orders. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Now all the work of Solomon was prepared — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "All the materials were procured, and in all points fitted and completed beforehand. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "So the house of God was perfected — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "This is now said, because the service of the temple was now put into this good order. The ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "work ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "was the main matter, not the ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "place: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "the temple was unfinished till all this was done. ",
        "children": []
